      <div class="msgContentFrame">So my friend showed me a screenshot of a armorer hitting lv 41 and having 32 million gil... <br /> <br />Soo how does an armorer actually make gil? I'm level 27 armorer making bronze cuiras, bronze plate boots, bronze gauntlets at 150k per and some iron armor under 70k per they don't sell. Only thing that does sell are things I've been making since level 15. Even so the majority of my gil is from battlecraft leves where I make over 100k every leve reset (24 glad).  <br /> <br />Anyone here able to make gil off of being an armorer other than having to use battlecraft leve money to buy shards for it and loose money in the end? <br /> <br />Cornelia server.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://www.enjin.com" rel="external nofollow" title="www.enjin.com">[img]<a href="http://sigs.enjin.com/sig-ffxiv/22931_bda9643ac6601722.png" title="http://sigs.enjin.com/sig-ffxiv/22931_bda9643ac6601722.png" rel="external nofollow">http://sigs.enjin.com/sig-ffxiv/22931_bda9643ac6601722.png</a>[/img]</a></div></div>
